            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Quicumque res Vareni in<lb break="no" n="2"/>volaverit si mul&amp;lt;i=R&amp;gt;er si mascel <lb n="3"/>sangu<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>no</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> suo solvat <lb n="4"/>et pecuni<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> quam exesuerit <lb n="5"/>Mercurio dona et Virtuti <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>acra</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gebet für Gerechtigkeit.</p>
